# FabricEase ðŸš€

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/fabricease.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/fabricease)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/fabricease.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/fabricease/)
